A	O
universal	O
directory	O
service	O
(	O
UDS	O
)	O
provides	O
the	O
communication	O
addresses	O
of	O
individuals	O
associated	O
with	O
numerous	O
different	O
institutions	O
,	O
and	O
can	O
be	O
accessed	O
via	O
more	O
than	O
one	O
communication	O
channel	O
.	O
A	O
UDS	O
server	O
communicates	O
with	O
one	O
or	O
more	O
data	O
sources	O
to	O
provide	O
directory	O
information	O
to	O
a	O
user	O
.	O
The	O
UDS	O
also	O
provides	O
supplemental	O
information	O
such	O
as	O
company	O
name	O
,	O
logo	O
,	O
and	O
specialty	O
.	O
The	O
UDS	O
can	O
be	O
accessed	O
via	O
numerous	O
communication	O
channels	O
including	O
the	O
internet	O
,	O
on-line	O
service	O
providers	O
,	O
wireless	O
devices	O
,	O
modem	O
,	O
dedicated	O
access	O
channels	O
,	O
voice	O
access	O
via	O
an	O
attendant	O
,	O
and	O
voice	O
access	O
via	O
a	O
speech	O
recognition	O
and	O
synthesis	O
system	O
.	O

