channels	O
.	O

SUMMARY	O
OF	O
THE	O
INVENTION	O
These	O
and	O
other	O
objects	O
of	O
the	O
invention	O
are	O
accomplished	O
in	O
accordance	O
with	O
the	O
principles	O
of	O
the	O
invention	O
by	O
providing	O
a	O
universal	O
directory	O
service	O
(	O
"	O
UDS	O
"	O
)	O
server	O
which	O
communicates	O
with	O
one	O
or	O
more	O
database	O
servers	O
containing	O
directory	O
information	O
relating	O
to	O
individuals	O
from	O
various	O
different	O
companies	O
.	O
In	O
a	O
preferred	O
embodiment	O
,	O
the	O
UDS	O
server	O
communicates	O
with	O
(	O
1	O
)	O
a	O
local	O
directory	O
server	O
containing	O
directory	O
information	O
relating	O
to	O
the	O
UDS	O
provider	O
and	O
additional	O
hosted	O
companies	O
,	O
(	O
2	O
)	O
on-line	O
directory	O
servers	O
maintained	O
by	O
corporations	O
from	O
which	O
the	O
provider	O
has	O
received	O
proper	O
permission	O
to	O
access	O
,	O
(	O
3	O
)	O
a	O
local	O
database	O
server	O
which	O
contains	O
directory	O
information	O
gathered	O
by	O
the	O
provider	O
and	O
third	O
parties	O
,	O
and	O
(	O
4	O
)	O
a	O
white	O
pages	O
directory	O
server	O
which	O
contains	O
directory	O
information	O
relating	O
to	O
private	O
individuals	O
.	O

The	O
UDS	O
server	O
can	O
be	O
accessed	O
via	O
the	O
internet	O
,	O
on-line	O
service	O
providers	O
,	O
wireless	O
communication	O
channels	O
,	O
dial-up	O
communication	O
channels	O
,	O
dedicated	O
communication	O
channels	O
,	O
telephone	O
connections	O
to	O
attendants	O
,	O
and	O
telephone	O
connections	O
to	O
a	O
voice	O
recognition	O
and	O
synthesis	O
system	O
.	O

In	O
addition	O
to	O
the	O
numerous	O
communication	O
addresses	O
of	O
an	O
individual	O
,	O
the	O
UDS	O
server	O
also	O
provides	O
supplemental	O
information	O
such	O
as	O
the	O
type	O
of	O
business	O
the	O
individual	O
or	O
company	O
is	O
engaged	O
in	O
,	O
specialties	O
or	O
particular	O
accomplishments	O
,	O
business	O
hours	O
,	O
prices	O
,	O
organizational	O
charts	O
,	O
responsibilities	O
of	O
the	O
individual	O
within	O
the	O
company	O
,	O
and	O
maps	O
logos	O
,	O
trademarks	O
,	O
and	O
other	O
graphical	O
images	O
.	O

This	O
invention	O
provides	O
a	O
convenient	O
,	O
inexpensive	O
,	O
and	O
quick	O
way	O
for	O
a	O
user	O
to	O
obtain	O
the	O
communication	O
addresses	O
of	O
someone	O
with	O
whom	O
they	O
wish	O
to	O
communicate	O
.	O
It	O
eliminates	O
the	O
need	O
to	O
make	O
repeated	O
telephone	O
calls	O
to	O
obtain	O
a	O
communications	O
address	O
,	O
and	O
the	O
need	O
to	O
maintain	O
printed	O
directories	O
.	O
Furthermore	O
,	O
